    "titleZh": "Bio-inspired Machine Learning",
    "titleEn": "Bio-inspired Machine Learning"
  },
  "2204.01691": {
    "id": "2204.01691",
    "version": "v2",
    "title": "Do As I Can, Not As I Say: Grounding Language in Robotic Affordances",
    "summary": "SayCan 明确提出语言语义与机器人可供性的统一接口问题，是当前 VLA 主线的代表性起点之一，后续 RT-1、PaLM-E、RT-2 与 OpenVLA 都在继续扩展它。",
